CHANGES0016: NormalForms.agda — quotient-level helpers added (457 lines, was 425)

Added QuotientSurjectivity module:
- cnfSurjQuotient: For any surjection q : freeBA A ↠ B, every element of B
  has a CNF representative. Uses cnfSurj + surjectivity of q.
- dnfSurjQuotient: Same for DNF.

These helpers make it easy to apply CNF/DNF normal forms to quotient Boolean
algebras (like NFinCofin's presentation = freeBA ℕ /Im relationsℕ).

No postulates. File compiles successfully.
